WEBVTT

00:00:04.812 --> 00:00:10.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now that I’m a little older,
And I’m a little bigger too,

00:00:10.937 --> 00:00:17.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m ready for some bigger things—
For the next ones I can do.

00:00:17.479 --> 00:00:23.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can sing, and I can answer,
And help to clean the Kingdom Hall.

00:00:23.645 --> 00:00:30.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ll visit with the older ones—
Get to know and love them all.

00:00:30.395 --> 00:00:36.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m ready for the next things,
The next big things for me.

00:00:36.895 --> 00:00:43.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m ready for the next things,
The next big things for me.

00:00:43.354 --> 00:00:49.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the ministry, I’m learning
To give a witness at the door

00:00:49.562 --> 00:00:53.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With scriptures I can learn to read.

00:00:53.187 --> 00:00:56.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can do all this and more!

00:00:56.562 --> 00:01:02.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m ready for the next things,
The next big things for me.

00:01:02.770 --> 00:01:10.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m ready for the next things,
The next big things for me.

